headline.print_headline: New York State Senator Concedes Tight Primary Race to Rangel
headline.main: New York State Senator Concedes Tight Primary Race to Rangel

lead_paragraph: A New York state senator on Thursday formally conceded to longtime incumbent U.S. Representative Charles Rangel in a razor-close Democratic primary for their congressional district.
